<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Quiz — 6: Linear Model (1)</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0a0e1a;
    --surface: #111827;
    --surface2: #1a2235;
    --surface3: #1e2d45;
    --border: #1e3050;
    --accent: #38bdf8;
    --accent2: #818cf8;
    --accent3: #34d399;
    --accent4: #f472b6;
    --warn: #fb923c;
    --text: #e2e8f0;
    --text2: #94a3b8;
    --text3: #64748b;
    --red: #f87171;
    --green: #34d399;
    --yellow: #fbbf24;
    --font-body: 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', 'Malgun Gothic', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    --font-code: 'Menlo', 'Courier New', monospace;
    --font-head: 'Impact', 'Arial Narrow', sans-serif;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  .page-header {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 28px 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .header-left {}
  .header-badge {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent4);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .header-title {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 22px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .header-right {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .score-box {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .score-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text3); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .score-val { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 22px; color: var(--accent); letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .btn-grade {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent2), var(--accent));
    color: #0a0e1a;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 9px;
    padding: 12px 26px;
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 15px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.1s;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .btn-grade:hover { opacity: 0.88; transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-reset {
    background: var(--surface2);
    color: var(--text2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 9px;
    padding: 12px 18px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-reset:hover { border-color: var(--text3); color: var(--text); }

  /* ── PROGRESS ── */
  .progress-bar {
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--border);
    position: relative;
  }
  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent2), var(--accent));
    width: 0%;
    transition: width 0.4s ease;
  }

  /* ── MAIN ── */
  .main {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 44px 28px 100px;
  }

  /* ── TYPE SECTION HEADER ── */
  .type-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin: 52px 0 24px;
  }
  .type-header:first-of-type { margin-top: 0; }
  .type-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 5px;
  }
  .type-badge.ox { background: rgba(251,146,60,0.15); color: var(--warn); border: 1px solid rgba(251,146,60,0.3); }
  .type-badge.mc { background: rgba(56,189,248,0.15); color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.3); }
  .type-badge.sa { background: rgba(129,140,248,0.15); color: var(--accent2); border: 1px solid rgba(129,140,248,0.3); }
  .type-badge.es { background: rgba(52,211,153,0.15); color: var(--accent3); border: 1px solid rgba(52,211,153,0.3); }
  .type-title {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .type-count {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text3);
  }

  /* ── QUESTION CARD ── */
  .q-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 13px;
    padding: 26px 28px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .q-card.answered-correct { border-color: rgba(52,211,153,0.45); }
  .q-card.answered-wrong   { border-color: rgba(248,113,113,0.45); }

  .q-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .q-num {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text3);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .diff {
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .slide-ref {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text3);
    background: var(--surface2);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .q-text {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .q-text code {
    font-family: var(--font-code);
    font-size: 13px;
    background: var(--surface2);
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--accent2);
  }

  /* ── MC OPTIONS ── */
  .mc-options {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 9px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .mc-opt {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface2);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    text-align: left;
    width: 100%;
    color: var(--text2);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .mc-opt:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--text); }
  .mc-opt.selected { border-color: var(--accent2); color: var(--text); background: rgba(129,140,248,0.08); }
  .mc-opt.correct  { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); background: rgba(52,211,153,0.08); }
  .mc-opt.wrong    { border-color: var(--red);   color: var(--red);   background: rgba(248,113,113,0.08); }
  .mc-opt.show-correct { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); background: rgba(52,211,153,0.06); }
  .mc-num {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 11px;
    min-width: 20px;
    color: var(--text3);
    padding-top: 1px;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .mc-opt.correct .mc-num, .mc-opt.show-correct .mc-num { color: var(--green); }
  .mc-opt.wrong .mc-num { color: var(--red); }
  .mc-opt.selected .mc-num { color: var(--accent2); }

  /* ── OX OPTIONS ── */
  .ox-options {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .ox-btn {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 16px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface2);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 24px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    color: var(--text2);
  }
  .ox-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .ox-btn[data-val="O"]:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }
  .ox-btn[data-val="X"]:hover { border-color: var(--red); color: var(--red); }
  .ox-btn.selected[data-val="O"] { border-color: var(--accent2); color: var(--accent2); background: rgba(129,140,248,0.1); }
  .ox-btn.selected[data-val="X"] { border-color: var(--accent2); color: var(--accent2); background: rgba(129,140,248,0.1); }
  .ox-btn.correct  { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); background: rgba(52,211,153,0.08); }
  .ox-btn.wrong    { border-color: var(--red);   color: var(--red);   background: rgba(248,113,113,0.08); }
  .ox-btn.show-correct { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); background: rgba(52,211,153,0.06); }

  /* ── SHORT ANSWER INPUT ── */
  .sa-input {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    resize: none;
  }
  .sa-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent2); }
  .sa-input.correct { border-color: var(--green); }
  .sa-input.wrong   { border-color: var(--red); }
  .sa-input:disabled { opacity: 0.7; cursor: not-allowed; }

  /* ── ESSAY ── */
  .essay-input {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    resize: vertical;
    min-height: 100px;
  }
  .essay-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent3); }
  .essay-input:disabled { opacity: 0.7; cursor: not-allowed; }

  /* ── ANSWER TOGGLE ── */
  .answer-toggle {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 7px;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text3);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .answer-toggle:hover { border-color: var(--text3); color: var(--text2); }
  .answer-toggle .arrow { transition: transform 0.2s; display: inline-block; }
  .answer-toggle.open .arrow { transform: rotate(90deg); }

  .answer-box {
    display: none;
    margin-top: 14px;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent2);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    padding: 14px 18px;
  }
  .answer-box.visible { display: block; }
  .answer-box .ans-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent2);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .answer-box .ans-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text2);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .answer-box .ans-text strong { color: var(--text); }
  .answer-box .ans-text code {
    font-family: var(--font-code);
    font-size: 12.5px;
    background: rgba(129,140,248,0.1);
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--accent2);
  }
  .result-icon {
    position: absolute;
    top: 22px;
    right: 22px;
    font-size: 20px;
    display: none;
  }
  .q-card.answered-correct .result-icon { display: block; }
  .q-card.answered-wrong .result-icon { display: block; }

  /* ── RESULT BANNER ── */
  .result-banner {
    display: none;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 32px 36px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .result-banner.visible { display: block; }
  .result-score-big {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 56px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .result-desc { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text2); }
  .result-bars {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .result-bar-item { text-align: center; }
  .result-bar-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text3); letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .result-bar-val { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 20px; }
  .val-correct { color: var(--green); }
  .val-wrong   { color: var(--red); }
  .val-skip    { color: var(--text3); }

  /* ── SCROLLBAR ── */
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--surface); }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--border); border-radius: 3px; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .page-header { padding: 18px 18px; }
    .main { padding: 28px 14px 80px; }
    .q-card { padding: 20px 18px; }
    .header-right { gap: 8px; }
    .btn-grade { padding: 10px 16px; font-size: 13px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header class="page-header">
  <div class="header-left">
    <div class="header-badge">📝 Quiz · Data Mining</div>
    <div class="header-title">6: Linear Model (1)</div>
  </div>
  <div class="header-right">
    <div class="score-box">
      <div class="score-label">점수</div>
      <div class="score-val" id="scoreVal">—</div>
    </div>
    <button class="btn-grade" onclick="gradeAll()">채점하기</button>
    <button class="btn-reset" onclick="resetAll()">초기화</button>
  </div>
</header>
<div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="progressFill"></div></div>

<div class="main">

  <!-- RESULT BANNER -->
  <div class="result-banner" id="resultBanner">
    <div class="result-score-big" id="resultScoreBig">0 / 25</div>
    <div class="result-desc" id="resultDesc">채점이 완료되었습니다.</div>
    <div class="result-bars">
      <div class="result-bar-item">
        <div class="result-bar-label">정답</div>
        <div class="result-bar-val val-correct" id="rCorrect">0</div>
      </div>
      <div class="result-bar-item">
        <div class="result-bar-label">오답</div>
        <div class="result-bar-val val-wrong" id="rWrong">0</div>
      </div>
      <div class="result-bar-item">
        <div class="result-bar-label">미응답</div>
        <div class="result-bar-val val-skip" id="rSkip">0</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════
       OX 문제 (7문제)
  ════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="type-header">
    <span class="type-badge ox">OX 문제</span>
    <span class="type-title">참 / 거짓 판별</span>
    <span class="type-count">Q1 ~ Q7</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Q1 -->
  <div class="q-card" id="q1">
    <div class="result-icon" id="ri1"></div>
    <div class="q-meta">
      <span class="q-num">Q1</span>
      <span class="diff">⭐</span>
      <span class="slide-ref">슬라이드 2</span>
    </div>
    <div class="q-text">선형 모델은 VC 차원이 작아 E_in에서 E_out으로 잘 일반화된다.</div>
    <div class="ox-options">
      <button class="ox-btn" data-q="1" data-val="O" onclick="selectOX(this)">O</button>
      <button class="ox-btn" data-q="1" data-val="X" onclick="selectOX(this)">X</button>
    </div>
    <button class="answer-toggle" onclick="toggleAnswer('a1', this)"><span class="arrow">▶</span> 정답 & 해설 보기</button>
    <div class="answer-box" id="a1">
      <div class="ans-label">정답</div>
      <div class="ans-text"><strong>O (참)</strong><br>선형 모델은 작은 VC 차원을 가지므로 학습 오류(E_in)에서 테스트 오류(E_out)로 잘 일반화(generalize)된다.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Q2 -->
  <div class="q-card" id="q2">
    <div class="result-icon" id="ri2"></div>
    <div class="q-meta">
      <span class="q-num">Q2</span>
      <span class="diff">⭐</span>
      <span class="slide-ref">슬라이드 4</span>
    </div>
    <div class="q-text">이진 분류 선형 모델에서 bias 항 w₀에 대응하는 입력 좌표는 x₀ = 0이다.</div>
    <div class="ox-options">
      <button class="ox-btn" data-q="2" data-val="O" onclick="selectOX(this)">O</button>
      <button class="ox-btn" data-q="2" data-val="X" onclick="selectOX(this)">X</button>
    </div>
    <button class="answer-toggle" onclick="toggleAnswer('a2', this)"><span class="arrow">▶</span> 정답 & 해설 보기</button>
    <div class="answer-box" id="a2">
      <div class="ans-label">정답</div>
      <div class="ans-text"><strong>X (거짓)</strong><br>bias 항 w₀에 대응하는 입력 좌표는 <strong>x₀ = 1</strong>이다. x₀ = 0이면 bias 항이 항상 0이 되어 의미가 없다.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Q3 -->
  <div class="q-card" id="q3">
    <div class="result-icon" id="ri3"></div>
    <div class="q-meta">
      <span class="q-num">Q3</span>
      <span class="diff">⭐⭐</span>
      <span class="slide-ref">슬라이드 7</span>
    </div>
    <div class="q-text">노이즈가 있는 비선형 분리 불가 데이터에서 E_in을 정확히 최소화하는 문제는 다항 시간(polynomial time) 내에 효율적으로 풀 수 있다.</div>
    <div class="ox-options">
      <button class="ox-btn" data-q="3" data-val="O" onclick="selectOX(this)">O</button>
      <button class="ox-btn" data-q="3" data-val="X" onclick="selectOX(this)">X</button>
    </div>
    <button class="answer-toggle" onclick="toggleAnswer('a3', this)"><span class="arrow">▶</span> 정답 & 해설 보기</button>
    <div class="answer-box" id="a3">
      <div class="ans-label">정답</div>
      <div class="ans-text"><strong>X (거짓)</strong><br>sign(·)와 [·]의 이산적(discrete) 특성 때문에 이 문제는 일반적으로 <strong>NP-hard</strong>이다. 알려진 효율적인 알고리즘이 없어 근사적으로 최소화하는 방법(예: Pocket Algorithm)을 사용한다.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Q4 -->
  <div class="q-card" id="q4">
    <div class="result-icon" id="ri4"></div>
    <div class="q-meta">
      <span class="q-num">Q4</span>
      <span class="diff">⭐⭐</span>
      <span class="slide-ref">슬라이드 9</span>
    </div>
    <div class="q-text">Pocket Algorithm은 PLA보다 빠르다. 왜냐하면 매 반복마다 전체 데이터셋에 대한 E_in 평가가 필요 없기 때문이다.</div>
    <div class="ox-options">
      <button class="ox-btn" data-q="4" data-val="O" onclick="selectOX(this)">O</button>
      <button class="ox-btn" data-q="4" data-val="X" onclick="selectOX(this)">X</button>
    </div>
    <button class="answer-toggle" onclick="toggleAnswer('a4', this)"><span class="arrow">▶</span> 정답 & 해설 보기</button>
    <div class="answer-box" id="a4">
      <div class="ans-label">정답</div>
      <div class="ans-text"><strong>X (거짓)</strong><br>Pocket Algorithm은 매 반복마다 <strong>전체 데이터셋에 대한 E_in 평가</strong>가 필요(line 4)하므로 PLA보다 훨씬 느리다 (much slower than PLA).</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Q5 -->
  <div class="q-card" id="q5">
    <div class="result-icon" id="ri5"></div>
    <div class="q-meta">
      <span class="q-num">Q5</span>
      <span class="diff">⭐</span>
      <span class="slide-ref">슬라이드 20</span>
    </div>
    <div class="q-text">통계학에서 "regression"이라는 용어는 y가 실수값(real-valued)임을 의미한다.</div>
    <div class="ox-options">
      <button class="ox-btn" data-q="5" data-val="O" onclick="selectOX(this)">O</button>
      <button class="ox-btn" data-q="5" data-val="X" onclick="selectOX(this)">X</button>
    </div>
    <button class="answer-toggle" onclick="toggleAnswer('a5', this)"><span class="arrow">▶</span> 정답 & 해설 보기</button>
    <div class="answer-box" id="a5">
      <div class="ans-label">정답</div>
